# Pet Adoption Finder

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
Pet Adoption Finder is a **JavaScript Single Page Application (SPA)** that helps users find adoptable pets by fetching real-time data from the **Petfinder API**. Users can filter pets by type, age, and size, view categorized listings, and save their favorite pets.

## ğŸ› ï¸ Features
- ğŸ” **Search & Filter:** Users can filter pets by **type (dog, cat, other), age, and size**.
- ğŸ“¦ **Categorization:** Pets are categorized into **Dogs, Cats, Other Pets, and Latest Arrivals**.
- â¤ï¸ **Favorite Pets:** Users can mark pets as favorites, stored in `localStorage`.
- ğŸš€ **Optimized API Requests:** Uses **access tokens with caching** to reduce unnecessary API calls.
- ğŸ“· **Image Filtering:** Pets without images are excluded to improve the user experience.
- âš¡ **Dynamic UI Updates:** Uses JavaScript to dynamically render pet listings based on API responses.

