## âš ï¸ Troubleshooting

### **1ï¸âƒ£ "Find Now" button is not working**
âœ… Ensure `id="find-now-btn"` exists in `index.html`.
âœ… Check browser console (`F12` â†’ Console) for errors.
âœ… Verify your **API credentials** are correct.

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Pets are not displaying correctly**
âœ… Check API token in `localStorage` (DevTools â†’ Application â†’ Storage).
âœ… Refresh the page to request a new token.
âœ… Confirm the API returns results (log `console.log(data.animals);`).

### **3ï¸âƒ£ "Favorite" button not saving pets**
âœ… Ensure `localStorage` is enabled in your browser.
âœ… Clear `localStorage` (`localStorage.clear();` in Console) and retry.

